description: Try our easy to follow Beef Bourguignon Pies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Beef Bourguignon Pies Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g simply heat slow cooked beef bourguignon

recipeInstructions.text: Place pies on the hot baking tray and bake for 25 minutes or until the pastry is golden. Serve with steamed veggies.
